installation note 

[How to install CASA in Ubuntu â€“ StarScientist](https://starscientist.org/how-to-install-casa-in-ubuntu/)

[official guide](https://casaguides.nrao.edu/index.php?title=Installing_CASA#Installing_CASA_on_Ubuntu)

installed version: 2020-Dec-24
CASA is releasing version 6.1 (Python 3) and CASA 5.7 (Python 2) simultaneously.

casa-6.1.2-7-pipeline-2020.1.0.36 => py3
casa-release-5.7.2-4.el7 => py2

add in your .bashrc

#casa-6_1_2 (py3)
alias casa-6_1_2="/opt/CASA-6_1_2/casa-6.1.2-7-pipeline-2020.1.0.36/bin/./casa"

#casa-5_7_2 (py2)
alias casa-5_7_2="/opt/CASA-5_7_2/casa-release-5.7.2-4.el7/bin/./casa"

#casa-5_6_2 (pipeline)
alias casa-5_6_2="/opt/casa-5.6.2-6-pipeline/casa-pipeline-release-5.6.2-6.el7/bin/./casa"
